'''Farxad''' ({{lang-en|happiness}}; {{lang-ar|سعادة}}) waa [[dareen]] [[maskax]]da ka yimaada taasi oo astaan u ah fiicni iyo wanaag. Farxadu waxay muhiim u tahay jiritaanka iyo nolosha [[noole|noolaha]] taasi oo saamayn ku yeelata [[caafimaad]]ka iyo jiritaanka noolahaasi.<ref>[http://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=happiness&a=*C.happiness-_*Word- Wordnet 3.0] (accessed 2011-Feb-24 via Wolfram Alpha)</ref>


„Waxaa barakaysan kuwa ereyga Ilaah maqla oo xajiya.” Dhisidda iimaanka runta ah waxay keentaa barakooyin badan. Run ahaan waa waddada nolol farxad leh hadda ilaa weligeedba.<ref>[https://www.jw.org/so/wargeysyada/maxaa-cusub/iimaan-run-ah/iimaanka-runta-ah-wuxuu-ku-siiyaa-farxad-weligeed-ah/ Iimaanka Runta ah Wuxuu ku Siiyaa Farxad Weligeed ah]</ref>.

